videos.description: RB Rodney Anderson bounces to the outside to run in for the easy 1-yard touchdown as Oklahoma goes up 7-0 on UTEP.

videos.description: Dimitri Flowers takes the handoff from Baker Mayfield and goes seven yards to the goal line in the second quarter, making the score 14-7 against UTEP.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Flowers finds easy route to end zone

videos.description: QB Baker Mayfield lobs it to Grant Calcaterra in the second quarter to cushion the Sooners' lead over the Miners 21-7.

videos.headline: Sooners' Mayfield throws first TD of season
